{"tid":1562738,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不如唱「願榮光歸香港」之餘, 唱埋美國國歌","createTime":"2019-09-12T06:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:50:22.000Z","uid":279932,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c53c283d9f1aa735eadfefed6f7b0e4810946995","tid":1562738,"uid":279932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"理性分析, 先由唱呢兩首歌既作用<br />\n其一: 激起戰意, keep住團火<br />\n第二: 對中共表示立場(亦可以激佢地)<br />\n<br />\n不過講到效用, 個人認為美國國歌對於第2點會更加有用<br />\n首先, 「願榮光歸香港」原先係一首戰歌, 雖然之後被捧成「國歌」, 但係終究唔係(而且中共方面亦可以spin), 理論上就好似你唱今天我、海闊天空 咁, 不過呢首係符號學上更代表到2019抗爭及其演變。<br />\n而講到符號學, 有一首歌更加可以代表到真香港人現時所既野&mdash;&mdash;爭取自由民主,、企係自由戰爭最前線, 個首歌就係美國國歌。<br />\n美國本身就代表住西方社會之首、民主及自由。所以舉美國旗先會有代表住爭取自由既意義, 美國就係呢個意識形態既top.<br />\n故此高歌美國國歌就係宣揚美國呢個符號所象徵既自由及民主, 係心理上亦可以再次強化番Hong Kong is not alone in this fight. (當然你話President Trump只係利用緊呢個情況, 呢個係當然既, 但務實去睇就係佢確實幫到手)<br />\n然後美國國歌亦唔可以比中共spin到去其他方面, 因為呢首確確實實係另一個國家既國歌, 而且個個國家既意識形態與中共個隻係兩極<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我個人覺得倒不如兩首都唱, 更加會有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且衰d講, 你想激死中共, 當然要唱埋呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1239a9c14cd15f227fa518ddb1a2ec2f72b89c4a","tid":1562738,"uid":279932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b3e657e56b20c94fba1ca9ec543147345da9e2","tid":1562738,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:36:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"590e43ec08dc4101f216c9e898324ea26475202e","tid":1562738,"uid":279932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"咁都有得負皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b27eb9998f715209acd0d6b9a5d1ff21d4faff","tid":1562738,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d793c9b732563156936688376a717df8f37bfb1","tid":1562738,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}